
No Single Point of Failure | Multi-server setup (Load balancers, Kubernetes, Auto Scaling Groups)
Fast Failover | Health checks, service discovery
Backup and Recovery | Database replication (master-slave / primary-replica)
Handle Server Crashes | Retry policies, queues, distributed logs
Handle Network Issues | Circuit breakers, retries with exponential backoff
Scalability | Stateless APIs + Horizontal scaling
